Package: libffi-mingw-w64-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libffi1-mingw-w64 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Portable foreign function interface library (mingw-w64 runtime)
 This package contains everything that is needed to run prgorams using libffi.

Package: libffi1-mingw-w64
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Portable foreign function interface library (mingw-w64 development files)
 This package contains the files that are needed in order to compile programs that use libffi.
